verbose_text: After treatment, the renal tissue TGF-beta1 protein expression level in groups CRF and CRF+ SAA was significantly higher than that in group S, respectively (P < 0.05), and the BMP-7 protein level in group CRF and Smad6 protein level in groups CRF and CRF+ SAA were significantly lower than those in group S, respectively (P < 0.05).
